 Cara [http://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/human-cyborg-steers-clear-of-drunk-women "Human cyborg steers clear of drunk women"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/lifestyle/entertainment/human-cyborg-steers-clear-of-drunk-women |date=20201111171401 }}, ''[[Strait_Times|Strait Times]]'', 22 May 2017.</ref>、聖莫尼卡藝術中心<ref>Frisach, Montse [http://www.elpuntavui.cat/noticia/article/5-cultura/19-cultura/534412-la-musica-del-mon.html "La Música del Món"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.elpuntavui.cat/noticia/article/5-cultura/19-cultura/534412-la-musica-del-mon.html |date=20141205004405 }} ''[[Avui|Avui]]'' 30 April 2012</ref>、普洛克畫廊<ref>Escobedo, Lee. [http://artsandculturetx.com/from-a-z-abracadabra-to-zombies/ "From A-Z"] {{Wayback|url=http://artsandculturetx.com/from-a-z-abracadabra-to-zombies/ |date=20151222201719 }} ''Arts and Culture Texas Magazine'' October 2015.</ref>以及[[美國|美國]]遠見藝術博物館<ref>Scharper, Julie [http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-10-06/entertainment/bs-ae-avam-20131006_1_technology-avam-rebecca-hoffberger "AVAM's 'Human, Soul & Machine' explores technology's power"] {{Wayback|url=http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-10-06/entertainment/bs-ae-avam-20131006_1_technology-avam-rebecca-hoffberger |date=20151222222553 }}, [[The_Baltimore_Sun|The Baltimore Sun]], 6 October 2013</ref>等地展出。

=== 聲音肖像 ===
為了創建聲音肖像，哈維森站在人的面前，將天線指向臉部的不同部分，然後寫下聽到的不同音符，然後創建聲音文件。他創作的現場肖像包括：[[菲利普·葛拉斯|菲利普·葛拉斯]]、[[勞勃·狄尼洛|勞勃·狄尼洛]]、[[艾瑞絲·愛普菲爾|艾瑞絲·愛普菲爾]]、[[奧利佛·史東|奧利佛·史東]]、[[史提夫·萊許|史提夫·萊許]]、[[波諾|波諾]]、[[伯茲·艾德林|伯茲·艾德林]]、索蘭芝・諾利斯、比爾·維奧拉、[[威爾斯親王查爾斯|威爾斯親王查爾斯]]、[[伍迪·艾倫|伍迪·艾倫]]<ref>Bergós, Mónica [http://www.elcorreo.com/vizcaya/v/20100515/gente/primer-cyborg-20100515.html "El primer 'cyborg'"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.elcorreo.com/vizcaya/v/20100515/gente/primer-cyborg-20100515.html |date=20171201034601 }}, ''[[El_Correo|El Correo]]'', 15 May 2010.</ref>、[[安東尼·塔皮埃斯|安東尼·塔皮埃斯]]、[[李奧納多·狄卡皮歐|李奧納多·狄卡皮歐]]、[[茱蒂·丹契|茱蒂·丹契]]<ref>Editor [http://abrigoportatil51.com/neil-harbisson.html#Panel2 "Neil Harbisson, Sentidos Cosmicos"] {{Wayback|url=http://abrigoportatil51.com/neil-harbisson.html#Panel2 |date=20201027210413 }}, Abrigo Portatil, Num.5. Brazil 2016.</ref>、[[魔比|魔比]]、[[詹姆斯·卡梅隆|詹姆斯·卡梅隆]]、[[彼得·布魯克|彼得·布魯克]]、[[艾爾·高爾|艾爾·高爾]]、[[提姆·柏內茲-李|提姆·柏內茲-李]]、梅茜・葛蕾、[[蓋爾·賈西亞·貝納|蓋爾·賈西亞·貝納]]<ref>Pesantes, Karla [http://www.vistazo.com/webpages/tecnologia/?id=17602 "Todos deberiamos queres ser cyborgs"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.vistazo.com/webpages/tecnologia/?id=17602 |date=20130603183221 }} ''[[Vistazo|Vistazo]]'' 19 October 2011</ref>、[[艾方索·柯朗|艾方索·柯朗]]、池田亮司、[[蓋布瑞·拜恩|蓋布瑞·拜恩]]<ref>Davies, Sally [http://nautil.us/issue/1/what-makes-you-so-special/encounters-with-the-posthuman "Encounters with the Posthuman"] {{Wayback|url=http://nautil.us/issue/1/what-makes-you-so-special/encounters-with-the-posthuman |date=20200105194436 }},''Nautilus'', 29 April 2013</ref>、[[阿爾貝二世_(摩納哥)|阿爾貝二世 (摩納哥)]]、[[史蒂夫·沃茲尼克|史蒂夫·沃茲尼克]]<ref>Bryant, Ross [http://www.dezeen.com/2013/11/20/interview-with-human-cyborg-neil-harbisson/ "People will start becoming technology says human cyborg"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dezeen.com/2013/11/20/interview-with-human-cyborg-neil-harbisson/ |date=20201111223056 }} "Dezeen Magazine" 20 November 2013</ref>、[[奧利佛·薩克斯|奧利佛·薩克斯]]以及[[喬治歐·莫瑞德|喬治歐·莫瑞德]]等人。<ref>{{cite tweet|user=NeilHarbisson|author=Neil Harbisson|number=459774110868852737|date=25 April 2014|title=Listening to @giorgiomoroder's moustache today at @Moogfest with @moonribas}}/photo/1/large "Neil Harbisson creating a sound portrait of Giorgio Moroder</ref>

